<doc id="1191997" wikidata="Q7660354" url="?curid=1191997" title="Syed Kalbe Hussain">
<text>Syed Kalbe Hussain Naqvi (मौलाना सैय्यद कल्बे हुसैन नक़वी) (مولانا سيد كلب حسين نقوى), also known as &quot;Kabban&quot;, was a Twelver Shia muslim cleric, scholar, preacher and a mujtahid from Lucknow, India. 

==Career==
He was a cleric, and was chief of the Shia scholars of South Asia during his time.

==Works==
* Duniya Ka Sarveshesth Hasti
* Gharze Shahadat

